general_exclusion_criteria:
History of non‑infectious pneumonitis/interstitial lung disease requiring steroids, current interstitial lung disease, or unresolved suspicious ILD on imaging;
Severe lung‑specific concurrent illness;
Uncontrolled infections necessitating IV antimicrobial therapy;
Pleural, pericardial, or abdominal effusions requiring invasive management (drainage, shunting, CART);
Known somatic EGFR/HER2 (ERBB2) activating DNA mutation lacking corresponding HER2 protein expression;
Primary diagnoses of breast adenocarcinoma, colonic/rectal adenocarcinoma, gastric adenocarcinoma, or non‑small cell lung cancer (for Part 1 cohorts) and similarly for Part 2 applicable exclusions;
Medical comorbidities interfering with safe study conduct.

